name','Κολύμβηση'),(305,'gre','Category',10,'name','Μαθήματα γυμναστικής και άσκησης'),(306,'gre','Category',9,'name','Διαχείριση του βάρους'),(307,'gre','Category',8,'name','Ασθένειες'),(308,'gre','Category',7,'name','Υγεία'),(309,'gre','Category',5,'name','Κοινωνικές ομάδες'),(311,'spa','NetworkCategory',35,'name','Input test category'),(0,'eng','Statement',1,'statement','I am interested in doing creative things'),(355,'spa','Statement',1,'statement','Estoy interesado en hacer cosas creativas'),(314,'eng','Statement',2,'statement','I would like to know more about social activities'),(315,'eng','Statement',2,'description','<p><strong>Social clubs </strong>may be linked to sports or cultural activities. Examples could include activities that you can enjoy with other people such as friendship groups, coffee mornings or church groups. Find one that is comfortable for you.</p>\r '),(316,'eng','Statement',3,'statement','I would like to learn more about my health'),(317,'eng','Statement',3,'description','<p>These are services or activities which can provide you with information on <strong>health conditions </strong>that can help support you with your health problems.</p>\r\n'),(318,'eng','Statement',4,'statement','I would like to lose weight'),(319,'eng','Statement',4,'description','<p>These are<strong> weight management </strong>services which can help you to lose weight and be healthy.</p>\r\n'),(320,'eng','Statement',5,'statement','I would like to get fitter'),(321,'eng','Statement',5,'description','<p>These are a range of ways for you to be fit and active such as <strong>fitness and exercise classes </strong>for all ages and abilities, <strong>swimming </strong>activities in the pool for the young and old and <strong>walking and outdoor activities</strong> which are good exercise for anyone regardless of age, income, location and ability. They are a great way to meet people in a relaxed environment. It is an easy activity to start doing, build up gradually and continue long-term.</p>\r\n'),(327,'eng','Statement',8,'description','<p>These are services which provide support for you including <strong>counselling </strong>where<strong> it allows a person to talk about their problems and feelings in a confidential and secure place and b</strong><strong>efriending which </strong>offers supportive, reliable relationships to people who may be lonely. People may become isolated because of ill health, disability or social disadvantage and so having someone to talk to or spend time with can be very important.</p>\r '),(326,'eng','Statement',8,'statement','I don\'t see other people very often'),(325,'eng','Statement',7,'description','<p>These are services which provide <strong>support for carers</strong> is in a number of ways from information and advice to the provision of grants and special break schemes.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(324,'eng','Statement',7,'statement','I look after someone e.g. a relative'),(329,'eng','Statement',9,'description','<p>These are groups and services that can help you with everyday practical problems and support independent living such as <strong>home support. </strong>This can be help with personal tasks, such as, bathing and washing, getting up and going to bed, shopping and managing finances and general household activities or odd jobs and <strong>financial and benefits advice </strong>which are services that allow individuals to gain access to community services, activities and resources that are not medical in nature. They offer <strong>confidential, impartial and independent information and advice.</strong> For example, help with debt worries and claiming benefits you may be entitled to; help with housing and employment problems; dealing with queries about consumer or tax issues; and advice on legal matters, immigration and family and personal matters.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(328,'eng','Statement',9,'statement','I would like to know more about things that will help me remain independent'),(330,'eng','Statement',10,'statement','I would like to know more about community transport'),(331,'eng','Statement',10,'description','<p>These are <strong>community transport</strong> services that offer support if you have limited mobility or have difficulty using public transport.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(332,'eng','Statement',11,'statement','I would like to help other people'),(333,'eng','Statement',11,'description','<p>By taking up things like<strong> volunteering opportunities</strong>, you can meet new people, have fun and build confidence and is a great way to give you the chance to make a difference in the community.</p>\r '),(375,'spa','Statement',11,'statement','Me gustaría ayudar a otras personas'),(376,'spa','Statement',11,'description','<p>Mediante las actividades de voluntariado puede encontrarse con otras personas, \n\npasarlo bien y ganar confianza y es una gran forma de que usted contribuya \n\npositivamente al desarrollo de su pueblo.</p>'),(374,'spa','Statement',10,'description','<p>Servicios que ofrecen información sobre el transporte. Si usted tiene problemas de \n\nmovilidad o dificultades para el uso del transporte public</p>'),(372,'spa','Statement',9,'statement','Me gustaría aprender cosas que me ayuden a ser más independiente'),(373,'spa','Statement',10,'statement','Me gustaría saber más sobre el transporte en mi pueblo'),(370,'spa','Statement',8,'statement','Me siento deprimido a veces y me gustaría poder hablar con alguien'),(371,'spa','Statement',9,'description','<p>Son actividades para que en su día a día, por ejemplo, en casa, tenga usted ayuda,\n\npor ejemplo para las tareas de la casa, lavarse, o ir a comprar. También puede ser \n\nayuda de consejo para cómo manejar sus problemas económicos y deudas, temas \n\nrelacionados con la familia, etc.</p>'),(369,'spa','Statement',8,'description','<p>Hay actividades que te ayudan mediante el consejo de otras personas o encontrarte \n\ncon personas en quienes puedes confiar como amigos. Para aquellas personas que \n\nse sienten solos/as. A veces el hablar con alguien ayuda a no sentirse solo por la \n\nenfermedad, discapacidad o por problemas sociales</p>'),(368,'spa','Statement',7,'statement','Me gustaría cuidar de otras personas. Por ejemplo, un familiar'),(367,'spa','Statement',7,'description','<p>Actividades que dan apoyo a cuidadores. Desde simplemente información a consejo y \n\nbecas.</p>'),(366,'spa','Statement',6,'statement','Me gustaría aprender a hacer cosas o hacer un curso'),(365,'spa','Statement',6,'description','<p>La educación y los cursos pueden ayudarle a mejorar en su forma de hablar, leer o\n\naprender informática.</p>'),(361,'spa','Statement',4,'statement','Me gustaría perder peso'),(362,'spa','Statement',4,'description','<p>Actividades que le ayudan a perder peso y a manternerse sano.</p>\r\n'),(363,'spa','Statement',5,'statement','Me gustaría estar más en forma'),(364,'spa','Statement',5,'description','<p>Actividades para mantenerle active y en forma como gimnasia, aerobic, caminar al aire libre. Son actividades f&aacute;ciles de hacer y que poco a poco va haciendo m&aacute;s para hacerlas durante mucho tiempo.</p>\r\n'),(356,'spa','Statement',1,'description','<p>Estas son actividades como leer y escribir, donde puedes hablar con otras personas   sobre libros, manualidades y actividades como cerámica, pintura, madera, teatro,   cantar y otras actividades que le puedes ayudar a encontrarse mejor y aumentar su   autoestima</p>'),(357,'spa','Statement',2,'statement','Me gustaría saber más sobre actividades sociales'),(358,'spa','Statement',2,'description','<p>Los clubes sociales pueden ser de deportes o de actividades culturales. Por ejemplo, \n\ntomar café con amigos o estar en un grupo en la parroquia.</p>'),(359,'spa','Statement',3,'statement','Me gustaría saber más sobre mi salud'),(360,'spa','Statement',3,'description','<p>Actividades que le pueden dar informaci&oacute;n sobre enfermedades y que le pueden ayudar con sus problemas de salud.</p>\r\n'),(354,'eng','Statement',1,'description','<p>These are activities or workshops where you can enjoy things like <strong>reading and creative writing </strong>clubs where you can discuss, debate, and exchange views about books and meet new friends who share a passion for books, <strong>arts and crafts </strong>activities where you can express yourself through painting, sculpture, and ceramics and <strong>drama and music </strong>activities that can help improve your confidence and self-esteem through learning a wide range of skills including drama, acting, singing, dancing, choreography, lighting and sound.</p>\r '),(378,'spa','Category',26,'name','Other health conditions'),(379,'spa','Category',4,'name','Drama y música'),(380,'spa','Category',3,'name','Arte y manualidades'),(381,'spa','Category',2,'name','Lectura y escritura'),(383,'spa','Category',23,'name','Voluntariado\n'),(384,'spa','Category',22,'name','Transporte\n'),(385,'spa','Category',21,'name','Asesoria financiera y burocrática\n'),(386,'spa','Category',20,'name','Ayuda a domicilio\n'),(387,'spa','Category',19,'name','Vida independiente'),(388,'spa','Category',18,'name','Support for you -  Befriending'),(389,'spa','Category',17,'name','Apoyo personalizado-consejo\n'),(390,'spa','Category',16,'name','Apoyo a cuidadores\n'),(391,'spa','Category',15,'name','Apoyo'),(392,'spa','Category',14,'name','Education and learning(sp)'),(393,'spa','Category',13,'name','Educación'),(394,'spa','Category',12,'name','Caminar y actividades al aire libre\n'),(395,'spa','Category',11,'name','Natación\n'),(396,'spa','Category',10,'name','Forma física y mantenimiento\n'),(397,'spa','Category',9,'name','Manejo peso'),(398,'spa','Category',8,'name','Estatus de salud\n'),(399,'spa','Category',7,'name','Salud'),(400,'spa','Category',5,'name','Club social'),(401,'spa','Category',24,'name','Oportunidades de voluntariado\n'),(402,'bul','Category',26,'name','Other health conditions'),(403,'bul','Category',4,'name','Драма и музика'),(404,'bul','Category',3,'name','Изкуство и занаяти'),(405,'bul','Category',2,'name','Литература и писателски клубове'),(406,'bul','Category',24,'name','Възможности да станеш доброволец '),(407,'bul','Category',23,'name','Доброволчество'),(408,'bul','Category',22,'name','Транспортни услуги от общината'),(409,'bul','Category',21,'name','Financial and benefits advice'),(410,'bul','Category',20,'name','Помощ в домакинството'),(411,'bul','Category',19,'name','Независимост'),(412,'bul','Category',18,'name','Подкрепа за Вас чрез сприятеляване'),(413,'bul','Category',17,'name','Подкрепа за Вас чрез консултиране'),(414,'bul','Category',16,'name','Подкрепа за оказващите помощ'),(415,'bul','Category',15,'name','Подкрепа'),(416,'bul','Category',14,'name','Образование и обучение'),(417,'bul','Category',13,'name','Обучение'),(418,'bul','Category',12,'name','Ходене и активен отдих на открито'),(419,'bul','Category',11,'name','Плуване'),(420,'bul','Category',10,'name','Фитнес и гимнастика'),(421,'bul','Category',9,'name','Поддържане на теглото'),(422,'bul','Category',8,'name','Клубове, свързани със здравето'),(423,'bul','Category',7,'name','Здраве'),(424,'bul','Category',5,'name','Клубове за социални дейности'),(425,'bul','Category',24,'name','Volunteering opportunities'),(426,'bul','Category',1,'name','Дейности'),(427,'eng','Category',1,'description','<p>Meeting different people and forming new friendships can help you feel good and improve your health and well being. It can also help reduce feelings of loneliness and boredom, allow you to share your experiences and (hopefully) make you smile.&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(428,'eng','Category',7,'description','<p>Information about health, weight management and physical activity is available to help you stay healthy and happy.</p>\r\n'),(429,'eng','Category',13,'description','<p>Whether you want to develop a new interest, learn a new skill, keep fit and healthy or simply have fun and make new friends there are classes for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(430,'eng','Category',15,'description','<p>Support can take different forms from emotional to physical assistance or companionship.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(431,'eng','Category',19,'description','<p>Practical and financial support is available to help you remain living in your own home and get around in the community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(432,'eng','Category',23,'description','<p>People can get a lot from volunteering. They do it for various reasons. People like the challenge or responsibility many volunteering opportunities can offer, and for some it&#39;s a way of occupying themselves positively.</p>\r '),(433,'eng','Page',1,'name','What is GENIE?'),(434,'eng','Page',1,'content','<p>GENIE is an online way to help you assess your health and social needs. Based on your responses, the internet programme will suggest local community services and activities that are likely to be of interest.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Keeping active, being involved in social activities and being able to find support (such as information about your health or help with everyday things) have been shown to have many health benefits. These include reduced anxiety; improved quality of life; and improved feelings about general health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As well as doing things for yourself, you may be interested in finding out what support is available in your local community. GENIE aims to:</p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n	<li>Help you think about what you can do to manage your health</li>\r\n	<li>Find ways you can increase the type of social contact you enjoy</li>\r\n	<li>Make you aware of local community support and activities</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>GENIE Questionnaire</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<p>Everyone is different and we need different things to help us manage our health and enjoy life. To help you find activities and support in your area we have developed the GENIE questionnaire which aims to help you think about what you can do to manage your health.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>As well as doing things for yourself, you can also plan ways to use support from your local community. GENIE can help you find local healthy activities such as exercise or diet groups. GENIE can also help you find activities that you might enjoy such as social or hobby groups.</p>\r\n\r\n<p><strong>Options for GENIE</strong></p>\r\n\r\n<ol>\r\n	<li>Click on the link below to fill in the short GENIE questionnaire. To find tailored results, fill in your details and then answer each question by selecting if you are interested to know more.</li>\r\n	<li>Search for services near you by entering your postcode.</li>\r\n	<li>Click on the categories above to search for services near you.</li>\r\n	<li>If you have used GENIE before, you can log in to see your results.</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n'),(435,'eng','Page',3,'name','About GENIE'),(436,'eng','Page',3,'content','<p>We know that information and courses designed to support people with long term conditions are not always helpful because they often do not take account of people&#39;s day to day life and circumstances.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How people manage long term conditions (such as diabetes, chronic kidney disease or chronic heart disease) is influenced by many things, such as feeling alone, being unemployed or caring for a relative.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The support available to people outside the health service (in particular local community organisations and groups and activities such as walking for health groups, art groups or lunch clubs) is being recognised as important in the management of long term conditions as it allows people to think about how to manage their health within the setting of their everyday life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GENIE&nbsp;has been developed to help individuals to find appropriate local activities to support them to make lifestyle changes, such as diet or exercise, and make the changes part of their everyday lives as well as to find fun and rewarding local activities.</p>\r\n'),(437,'eng','Page',4,'name','Contact Us'),(438,'eng','Page',4,'content','<p>GENIE TEAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Faculty of Health Sciences<br />\r\nUniversity of Southampton<br />\r\nHighfield<br />\r\nSouthampton<br />\r\nSO17 1BJ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>email:</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ivaylo Vassilev: I.I.Vassilev@soton.ac.uk</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Liz James: E.P.James@soton.ac.uk</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Claire Reidy: C.M.Reidy@soton.ac.uk</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(439,'bul','Page',1,'name','Какво е GENIE?'),(440,'bul','Page',1,'content','<p>GENIE e онлайн средство, което ще Ви помогне да оцените Вашето здраве и Вашите социални нужди. Въз основа на Вашите отговори тази интернет програма ще Ви предложи услугите и дейностите на местната общност, които вероятно ще Ви заинтересуват.<br />\r\nДоказано е, че поддържането на активност, включването в социални дейности и възможността да се намери подкрепа (като напр. информация за Вашето здраве или да получите помощ в ежедневните си дейности)&nbsp; са много полезни за здравето. Тези ползи включват намаляване на&nbsp; тревожността, подобряване на качеството на живот и чувство за по-добро общо здравословно състояние.<br />\r\nКато правите неща за себе си, може би се интересувате от намиране на подкрепа, която се предлага във Вашата местна общност. GENIE има за цел:<br />\r\n- Да Ви помогне да помислите какво можете да направите, за да управлявате Вашето здраве.<br />\r\n- Да намерите начин да увеличите вида на социалните контакти, които Ви радват.<br />\r\n-Да сте осведомени за подкрепата и дейностите на местната общност.<br />\r\nВсеки е различен и се нуждаем от различни неща, които да ни помогнат да управляваме своето здраве и да се радваме на живота. За да Ви помогнем да намерите дейности и подкрепа във Вашия район, ние сме разработили&nbsp; въпросника на GENIE, който има за цел да Ви помогне да помислите какво&nbsp; можете да направите, за да управлявате Вашето здраве.<br />\r\nКато правите неща за себе си, може да планирате начини да използвате подкрепа от Вашата местна общност.&nbsp; GENIE може да Ви помогне да намерите местни дейности за здравословен живот като групи за гимнастика или за диети. GENIE също може да Ви помогне да намерите&nbsp; дейности, които&nbsp; могат да Ви доставят радост - като участие в социални или хоби групи.<br />\r\nОпции за GENIE<br />\r\n1.&nbsp;Кликнете върху линка по-долу, за да попълните краткия въпросник&nbsp; на GENIE. За да намерите персонализирани за Вас резултати, попълнете своите данни и след това отговорете на всеки въпрос като изберете подходящия отговор, ако се интересувате от повече информация.<br />\r\n2.&nbsp; Търсене на услуги близо до Вас чрез въвеждане на Вашия пощенски код.<br />\r\n3.&nbsp;Кликнете върху категориите по-горе за търсене на услуги близо до Вас<br />\r\n4.&nbsp;Ако вече сте използвали GENIE, можете да влезете в системата, за да видите резултатите си.</p>\r\n'),(441,'bul','Page',3,'name','За GENIE'),(442,'bul','Page',3,'content','<p>We know that information and courses designed to support people with long term conditions are not always helpful because they often do not take account of people&#39;s day to day life and circumstances.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>How people manage long term conditions (such as diabetes, chronic kidney disease or chronic heart disease) is influenced by many things, such as feeling alone, being unemployed or caring for a relative.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>The support available to people outside the health service (in particular local community organisations and groups and activities such as walking for health groups, art groups or lunch clubs) is being recognised as important in the management of long term conditions as it allows people to think about how to manage their health within the setting of their everyday life.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>GENIE&nbsp;has been developed to help individuals to find appropriate local activities to support them to make lifestyle changes, such as diet or exercise, and make the changes part of their everyday lives as well as to find fun and rewarding local activities.</p>\r\n'),(443,'bul','Page',4,'name','Contact Us'),(444,'bul','Page',4,'content','<p>GENIE TEAM</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Faculty of Health Sciences<br />\r\nUniversity of Southampton<br />\r\nHighfield<br />\r\nSouthampton<br />\r\nSO17 1BJ</p>\r\n\r\n<p>email: Ivaylo Vassilev: <a href=\"mailto:I.I.Vassilev@soton.ac.uk\">I.I.Vassilev@soton.ac.uk</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Liz James: <a href=\"mailto:ej1q07@soton.ac.uk\">ej1q07@soton.ac.uk</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; Claire Reidy: <a href=\"mailto:C.M.Reidy@soton.ac.uk\">C.M.Reidy@soton.ac.uk</a></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(445,'gre','Page',1,'name','Τι είναι η GENIE;'),(446,'gre','Page',1,'content','<p>&Eta; GENIE &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&iota; έ&nu;&alpha;&sigmaf; online &tau;&rho;ό&pi;&omicron;&sigmaf; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &nu;&alpha; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf; &beta;&omicron;&eta;&theta;ή&sigma;&epsilon;&iota; &nu;&alpha; &alpha;&pi;&omicron;&kappa;&tau;ή&sigma;&epsilon;&tau;&epsilon; &pi;&rho;ό&sigma;&beta;&alpha;&sigma;&eta; &sigma;&tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &kappa;&omicron;&iota;&nu;&omega;&nu;&iota;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &iota;&alpha;&tau;&rho;&iota;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf; &alpha;&nu;ά&gamma;&kappa;&epsilon;&sigmaf;. &Beta;&alpha;&sigma;&iota;&zeta;ό&mu;&epsilon;&nu;&omicron;&iota; &sigma;&tau;&iota;&sigmaf; &alpha;&pi;&alpha;&nu;&tau;ή&sigma;&epsilon;&iota;&sigmaf; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf;, &tau;&omicron; &pi;&rho;ό&gamma;&rho;&alpha;&mu;&mu;&alpha; &mu;έ&sigma;&omega; &tau;&omicron;&upsilon; &delta;&iota;&alpha;&delta;&iota;&kappa;&tau;ύ&omicron;&upsilon; &theta;&alpha; &pi;&rho;&omicron;&tau;&epsilon;ί&nu;&epsilon;&iota; &tau;&omicron;&pi;&iota;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &kappa;&omicron;&iota;&nu;&omicron;&tau;&eta;&kappa;έ&sigmaf; &upsilon;&pi;&eta;&rho;&epsilon;&sigma;ί&epsilon;&sigmaf; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &delta;&rho;&alpha;&sigma;&tau;&eta;&rho;&iota;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &pi;&omicron;&upsilon; &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&io