mbda;&omicron;&upsilon;&sigmaf;, &upsilon;&pi;ά&rho;&chi;&omicron;&upsilon;&nu; &mu;&alpha;&theta;ή&mu;&alpha;&tau;&alpha; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf;.</p>\r\n'),(466,'gre','Category',15,'description','<p>&Upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&sigma;&tau;ή&rho;&iota;&xi;&eta; &mu;&pi;&omicron;&rho;&epsilon;ί &nu;&alpha; &lambda;ά&beta;&epsilon;&iota; &delta;&iota;ά&phi;&omicron;&rho;&epsilon;&sigmaf; &mu;&omicron;&rho;&phi;έ&sigmaf;, &alpha;&pi;ό &tau;&eta; &sigma;&upsilon;&nu;&alpha;&iota;&sigma;&theta;&eta;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&iota;&kappa;ή, &tau;&eta; &sigma;&omega;&mu;&alpha;&tau;&iota;&kappa;ή &beta;&omicron;ή&theta;&epsilon;&iota;&alpha; ή &tau;&eta; &sigma;&upsilon;&nu;&tau;&rho;&omicron;&phi;&iota;&kappa;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;&alpha;.</p>\r\n'),(467,'gre','Category',19,'description','<p>&Pi;&rho;&alpha;&kappa;&tau;&iota;&kappa;ή &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &omicron;&iota;&kappa;&omicron;&nu;&omicron;&mu;&iota;&kappa;ή &upsilon;&pi;&omicron;&sigma;&tau;ή&rho;&iota;&xi;&eta; &epsilon;ί&nu;&alpha;&iota; &delta;&iota;&alpha;&theta;έ&sigma;&iota;&mu;&eta; &gamma;&iota;&alpha; &nu;&alpha; &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf; &beta;&omicron;&eta;&theta;ή&sigma;&epsilon;&iota; &nu;&alpha; &sigma;&upsilon;&nu;&epsilon;&chi;ί&sigma;&epsilon;&tau;&epsilon; &nu;&alpha; &zeta;&epsilon;ί&tau;&epsilon; &sigma;&tau;&omicron; &delta;&iota;&kappa;ό &sigma;&alpha;&sigmaf; &sigma;&pi;ί&tau;&iota; &kappa;&alpha;&iota; &sigma;&tau;&eta;&nu; &kappa;&omicron;&iota;&nu;ό&tau;&eta;&tau;&alpha;.</p>\r\n'),(468,'gre','Category',23,'description','<p>Οι άνθρωποι μπορούν να πάρουν πολλά από τον εθελοντισμό. Το κάνουν για διάφορους λόγους, όπως οι προκλήσεις ή ευθύνες που πολλές εθελοντικές δραστηριότητες μπορεί να προσφέρουν, και για κάποιους είναι ένας τρόπος να δραστηριοποιούνται και οι ίδιοι θετικά.</p>'),(469,'bul','Category',1,'description','<p>Meeting different people and forming new friendships can help you feel good and improve your health and well being. It can also help reduce feelings of loneliness and boredom, allow you to share your experiences and (hopefully) make you smile.&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(470,'bul','Category',7,'description','<p>Information about health, weight management and physical activity is available to help you stay healthy and happy.</p>\r\n'),(471,'bul','Category',13,'description','<p>Whether you want to develop a new interest, learn a new skill, keep fit and healthy or simply have fun and make new friends there are classes for you.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(472,'bul','Category',15,'description','<p>Support can take different forms from emotional to physical assistance or companionship.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(473,'bul','Category',19,'description','<p>Practical and financial support is available to help you remain living in your own home and get around in the community.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(474,'bul','Category',23,'description','<p>People can get a lot from volunteering. They do it for various reasons. People like the challenge or responsibility many volunteering opportunities can offer, and for some it&#39;s a way of occupying themselves positively.</p>\r '),(476,'bul','Statement',6,'description','<p><strong>Education and learning </strong>services can help you with things like improving your spoken English, reading or writing, or to develop your computer skills.</p>\r '),(477,'bul','Statement',6,'statement','I would like to learn new skills or complete a course'),(478,'bul','Statement',1,'statement','I am interested in doing creative things'),(479,'bul','Statement',2,'statement','I would like to know more about social activities'),(480,'bul','Statement',2,'description','<p><strong>Social clubs </strong>may be linked to sports or cultural activities. Examples could include activities that you can enjoy with other people such as friendship groups, coffee mornings or church groups. Find one that is comfortable for you.</p>\r '),(481,'bul','Statement',3,'statement','I would like to learn more about my health'),(482,'bul','Statement',3,'description','<p>These are services or activities which can provide you with information on <strong>health conditions </strong>that can help support you with your health problems.</p>\r\n'),(483,'bul','Statement',4,'statement','I would like to lose weight'),(484,'bul','Statement',4,'description','<p>These are<strong> weight management </strong>services which can help you to lose weight and be healthy.</p>\r\n'),(485,'bul','Statement',5,'statement','I would like to get fitter'),(486,'bul','Statement',5,'description','<p>These are a range of ways for you to be fit and active such as <strong>fitness and exercise classes </strong>for all ages and abilities, <strong>swimming </strong>activities in the pool for the young and old and <strong>walking and outdoor activities</strong> which are good exercise for anyone regardless of age, income, location and ability. They are a great way to meet people in a relaxed environment. It is an easy activity to start doing, build up gradually and continue long-term.</p>\r\n'),(487,'bul','Statement',8,'description','<p>These are services which provide support for you including <strong>counselling </strong>where<strong> it allows a person to talk about their problems and feelings in a confidential and secure place and b</strong><strong>efriending which </strong>offers supportive, reliable relationships to people who may be lonely. People may become isolated because of ill health, disability or social disadvantage and so having someone to talk to or spend time with can be very important.</p>\r '),(488,'bul','Statement',8,'statement','I don\'t see other people very often'),(489,'bul','Statement',7,'description','<p>These are services which provide <strong>support for carers</strong> is in a number of ways from information and advice to the provision of grants and special break schemes.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(490,'bul','Statement',7,'statement','I look after someone e.g. a relative'),(491,'bul','Statement',9,'description','<p>These are groups and services that can help you with everyday practical problems and support independent living such as <strong>home support. </strong>This can be help with personal tasks, such as, bathing and washing, getting up and going to bed, shopping and managing finances and general household activities or odd jobs and <strong>financial and benefits advice </strong>which are services that allow individuals to gain access to community services, activities and resources that are not medical in nature. They offer <strong>confidential, impartial and independent information and advice.</strong> For example, help with debt worries and claiming benefits you may be entitled to; help with housing and employment problems; dealing with queries about consumer or tax issues; and advice on legal matters, immigration and family and personal matters.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(492,'bul','Statement',9,'statement','I would like to know more about things that will help me remain independent'),(493,'bul','Statement',10,'statement','I would like to know more about community transport'),(494,'bul','Statement',10,'description','<p>These are <strong>community transport</strong> services that offer support if you have limited mobility or have difficulty using public transport.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(495,'bul','Statement',11,'statement','I would like to help other people'),(496,'bul','Statement',11,'description','<p>By taking up things like<strong> volunteering opportunities</strong>, you can meet new people, have fun and build confidence and is a great way to give you the chance to make a difference in the community.</p>\r '),(497,'bul','Statement',1,'description','<p>These are activities or workshops where you can enjoy things like <strong>reading and creative writing </strong>clubs where you can discuss, debate, and exchange views about books and meet new friends who share a passion for books, <strong>arts and crafts </strong>activities where you can express yourself through painting, sculpture, and ceramics and <strong>drama and music </strong>activities that can help improve your confidence and self-esteem through learning a wide range of skills including drama, acting, singing, dancing, choreography, lighting and sound.</p>\r '),(498,'gre','Statement',6,'description','<p><strong>Education and learning </strong>services can help you with things like improving your spoken English, reading or writing, or to develop your computer skills.</p>\r '),(499,'gre','Statement',6,'statement','Θα ήθελα να μάθω νέες δεξιότητες ή να ολοκληρώσω μία σειρά μαθημάτων'),(500,'gre','Statement',1,'statement','Με ενδιαφέρει να κάνω δημιουργικά πράγματα'),(501,'gre','Statement',2,'statement','Θα ήθελα να μάθω περισσότερα σχετικά με διάφορες κοινωνικές δραστηριότητες'),(502,'gre','Statement',2,'description','<p><strong>Social clubs </strong>may be linked to sports or cultural activities. Examples could include activities that you can enjoy with other people such as friendship groups, coffee mornings or church groups. Find one that is comfortable for you.</p>\r '),(503,'gre','Statement',3,'statement','Θα ήθελα να μάθω περισσότερα σχετικά με την υγεία μου'),(504,'gre','Statement',3,'description','<p>These are services or activities which can provide you with information on <strong>health conditions </strong>that can help support you with your health problems.</p>\r\n'),(505,'gre','Statement',4,'statement','Θα ήθελα να χάσω κιλά'),(506,'gre','Statement',4,'description','<p>These are<strong> weight management </strong>services which can help you to lose weight and be healthy.</p>\r\n'),(507,'gre','Statement',5,'statement','Θα ήθελα να αποκτήσω καλύτερη φυσική κατάσταση'),(508,'gre','Statement',5,'description','<p>These are a range of ways for you to be fit and active such as <strong>fitness and exercise classes </strong>for all ages and abilities, <strong>swimming </strong>activities in the pool for the young and old and <strong>walking and outdoor activities</strong> which are good exercise for anyone regardless of age, income, location and ability. They are a great way to meet people in a relaxed environment. It is an easy activity to start doing, build up gradually and continue long-term.</p>\r\n'),(509,'gre','Statement',8,'description','<p>These are services which provide support for you including <strong>counselling </strong>where<strong> it allows a person to talk about their problems and feelings in a confidential and secure place and b</strong><strong>efriending which </strong>offers supportive, reliable relationships to people who may be lonely. People may become isolated because of ill health, disability or social disadvantage and so having someone to talk to or spend time with can be very important.</p>\r '),(510,'gre','Statement',8,'statement','Δεν συναναστρέφομαι τακτικά με άλλα άτομα\n'),(511,'gre','Statement',7,'description','<p>These are services which provide <strong>support for carers</strong> is in a number of ways from information and advice to the provision of grants and special break schemes.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(512,'gre','Statement',7,'statement','Φροντίζω κάποιον (φροντιστής) π.χ. έναν συγγενή'),(513,'gre','Statement',9,'description','<p>These are groups and services that can help you with everyday practical problems and support independent living such as <strong>home support. </strong>This can be help with personal tasks, such as, bathing and washing, getting up and going to bed, shopping and managing finances and general household activities or odd jobs and <strong>financial and benefits advice </strong>which are services that allow individuals to gain access to community services, activities and resources that are not medical in nature. They offer <strong>confidential, impartial and independent information and advice.</strong> For example, help with debt worries and claiming benefits you may be entitled to; help with housing and employment problems; dealing with queries about consumer or tax issues; and advice on legal matters, immigration and family and personal matters.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(514,'gre','Statement',9,'statement','Θα ήθελα να μάθω περισσότερα πράγματα για με τον τρόπο που θα μπορούσα να παραμείνω ανεξάρτητος για περισσότερο καιρό \n'),(515,'gre','Statement',10,'statement','Θα ήθελα να μάθω περισσότερα για τα δρομολόγια των μέσων μαζικής μεταφοράς\n'),(516,'gre','Statement',10,'description','<p>These are <strong>community transport</strong> services that offer support if you have limited mobility or have difficulty using public transport.&nbsp;</p>\r '),(517,'gre','Statement',11,'statement','Θα ήθελα να βοηθήσω τους συνανθρώπους μου\n'),(518,'gre','Statement',11,'description','<p>By taking up things like<strong> volunteering opportunities</strong>, you can meet new people, have fun and build confidence and is a great way to give you the chance to make a difference in the community.</p>\r '),(519,'gre','Statement',1,'description','<p>These are activities or workshops where you can enjoy things like <strong>reading and creative writing </strong>clubs where you can discuss, debate, and exchange views about books and meet new friends who share a passion for books, <strong>arts and crafts </strong>activities where you can express yourself through painting, sculpture, and ceramics and <strong>drama and music </strong>activities that can help improve your confidence and self-esteem through learning a wide range of skills including drama, acting, singing, dancing, choreography, lighting and sound.</p>\r '),(520,'eng','NetworkType',1,'name','Diverse'),(521,'eng','NetworkType',1,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>diverse</strong></em> type of network are in contact with a range of people including voluntary or community groups. They are in frequent contact with some, but not all network members, able to rely on a range of network member support and have different options when choosing the most appropriate and acceptable type of network involvement.</p>\r\n'),(522,'eng','NetworkType',2,'name','Family & Friend Centered'),(523,'eng','NetworkType',2,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>family and friend centred</strong></em> network are in regular contact with both <strong>friends</strong> and <strong>family members</strong>, but are not very involved with hobby or community groups and activities. They are able to rely on substantial and wide ranging support from family and friends and to have some, but not very diverse, options when choosing an appropriate and acceptable type of network involvement.</p>\r '),(524,'eng','NetworkType',3,'name','Friend Centered'),(525,'eng','NetworkType',3,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>friend centred </strong></em>network are in regular contact with friends, but not family members, and are not very involved with hobby or community groups and activities. They are able to rely on substantial and wide ranging support from their friends and to have some, but not very diverse, options when choosing an appropriate and acceptable type of network involvement.</p>\r\n'),(526,'eng','NetworkType',4,'name','Family Centered'),(527,'eng','NetworkType',4,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>family centred</strong></em> network are in regular contact with family members, but not friends, and are very unlikely to be involved with hobby or community groups and activities. They are able to rely on substantial and wide ranging support from their family members, but have limited options when choosing an appropriate and acceptable type of network involvement. People with such a network sometimes face additional challenges with illness management when family members do not have a good understanding of their illness.&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(528,'eng','NetworkType',5,'name','Family & Friend Supported'),(529,'eng','NetworkType',5,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>family and friend supported </strong></em>network are in contact with both friends and family members, but the contact may be infrequent. They are able to rely on some support from family and friends, but access to such support is not always available and could meet only some of the person&rsquo;s health and practical support needs.&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(530,'eng','NetworkType',6,'name','Friend Supported'),(531,'eng','NetworkType',6,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>friend supported </strong></em>network are only in contact with friends, but not family members. Their contacts with friends may be infrequent. While they may rely on some support from friends, access to such support may not be available and could meet only some of the person&rsquo;s health and practical support needs. People with such networks might need additional support with practical day-to-day tasks.</p>\r\n'),(532,'eng','NetworkType',7,'name','Family Supported'),(533,'eng','NetworkType',7,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>family supported </strong></em>network are only in contact with family members, but not friends. Their contacts with family members may be infrequent. While they may rely on some support from family members, access to such support might not be available and meet only some of the person&rsquo;s health and practical support needs. People with such a network sometimes face additional challenges with illness management when family members do not have a good understanding of their illness.&nbsp;</p>\r\n'),(534,'eng','NetworkType',8,'name','Small'),(535,'eng','NetworkType',8,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>small </strong></em>network only have a limited number of contacts and are rarely in contact with their network members. They will only have very ad hoc and rare access to health related support and to support with &nbsp;completing day-to-day practical tasks.</p>\r\n'),(536,'eng','NetworkType',9,'name','Very small '),(537,'eng','NetworkType',9,'description','<p>People with a <em><strong>very small </strong></em>network have a very limited or no contact with network members. They are almost exclusively dependent on