lton/index.html','Helio Fitness is a new state of the art fitness club that opened in January 2011. From as little as £18.95 per month for full gym membership, our budget model enables anyone from any background to have the opportunity to train, providing state of the art facilities. Our family run business will make sure everyone feels welcome and comfortable in their training environment. We pride ourselves on excellent customer service to provide members with a friendly atmosphere in order to enhance their training experience. Helio Fitness offers affordable fitness for all, with over 170 state of the art pieces of equipment, including the latest Kettlebells and the TRX suspension.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,150,1,1,NULL,NULL,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'helio-bolton'),(258,'Highfield Hall Community Centre','Shelly','Highfield Hall','Highfield Road','Farnworth','Bolton','BL4 0AW','01204 862100',NULL,'http://www.highfield-hall.org/','Activities and services include Bolton Art Circle (art club), Broadoaks Nursery, Jazz Dance Fitness Classes, Streetdance Fitness Classes, Wiggle & Jiggle Toddler and Parent Group, Yoga Sessions (Friday 7-8.30pm) and Zumba Classes (Wednesdays 7-8pm and Thursdays 8-9pm. £3.50 each class.)',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,150,1,1,53.546753,-2.421173,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'highfield-hall-community-centre'),(259,'Horwich Leisure Centre',NULL,'Victoria Road','Horwich',NULL,'Bolton','BL6 5PY','01204 334488',NULL,'http://www.boltonleisure.com/horwich','Horwich Leisure Centre is a contemporary health and fitness venue. We offer a range of facilities including a swimming pool, teaching pool, fitness suites, large sports hall, all weather pitches and meeting rooms. May have a weight management programme in place soon.',NULL,'SwimInBolton','https://www.facebook.com/SwimInBolton',1,150,1,1,53.593705,-2.540165,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'horwich-leisure-centre'),(260,'Ke