pletely flexible and affordable.',NULL,'','https://www.facebook.com/pages/Outline-Fitness/134951876540002',1,150,1,1,53.569052,-2.428095,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'outline-fitness'),(262,'Samberjacks',NULL,'1st and 2nd Floor','128-136 Bradshawgate','Bolton','Bolton','BL2 1AY','07597 311395','info@samberjacks.com ','http://www.samberjacks.com/','Dance, fitness and music. Our fully qualified dance teachers have around 18 years experience teaching dance in Bolton, Atherton and Manchester. We will have a large range of classes available from the new studios when we open in January 2012. At Samberjacks we believe that everyone is equal, whatever your age (0 to 100+ years) or ability. Although nothing is compulsory, there are opportunities to take part in exams, shows, competitions or carnivals (if you want to), although the main emphasis is fun and laughter. Everyone is welcome, whether you wish to attend a weekly class as a hobby, compete or make dancing a possible career. We also offer variety of activities including: Adult dance aerobics, ballroom, Latin American and Cuban Latino, line dancing, and zumba which include: our unique baby & pre-school programme, teacher training courses, private lessons, wedding choreography, birthday parties, holiday clubs + much more. Our extensively trained staff are also available to run sessions in nurseries and schools. Please contact us for further information or to discuss your requirements. Classes start from just £3 per week.',NULL,'Samberjacks','https://www.facebook.com/Samberjacks',1,150,1,1,53.576335,-2.425741,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'samberjacks'),(263,'Ashton Leisure Centre',NULL,'Old Road','Ashton-in-Makerfield',NULL,'Wigan','WN4 9TP','01942 720826',NULL,'http://www.wlct.org/Sport-and-Healthy-Living/activelife/ashton-leisure-centre.htm','Facilities at this popular site include recently refurbished large and small swimming pools offering a wide range of p