g','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'contact-the-elderly'),(396,'Halliwell Befriending Service','Carol','Halliwell Road Free Church','Halliwell',NULL,'Bolton','BL1 8DE','01204 840808','info@halliwelbefriendingservice.co.uk','http://www.localdirectory.bolton.gov.uk/ProviderDetails.aspx?ProviderID=506769','This service has expanded to cover Halliwell, Heaton and Sharples Areas. Services include befriending, escorted shopping, sit in service for carers, social events so people can make new friends and keep in touch with their community.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,150,1,1,53.593849,-2.442614,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'halliwell-befriending-service'),(397,'Home Instead Senior Care Bolton','David Deller','Office 18 112A-116','Hamill House','Chorley New Road','Bolton','BL1 4DH','01204 498949','david.deller@homeinstead.co.uk','http://www.homeinstead.co.uk/bolton','Home Instead Senior Care provides quality care for people in their own homes. Care is personalised for each individual with a broad range of services available to help people remain independent. These range from companionship, accompanying on trips out, home help, intermediate care, personal care, respite care and specialist Dementia and Alzheimer\'s care. Our service is available 24 hours per day.',NULL,'','https://www.facebook.com/pages/Home-Instead-Senior-Care-Bolton/171999296171516',1,150,1,1,53.579801,-2.466971,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'home-instead-senior-care-bolton'),(398,'Horwich Visiting Service','Pauline Chadwick','Horwich Clinic','Jones Street','Horwich','Bolton','BL6 7AJ','01204 669408',NULL,'http://horwichvisitingservice.wordpress.com/','Offers friendship to anyone who is elderly, isolated or housebound and who live in Horwich. Accepts referrals from family, GPs, and social workers. We also offer an assisted shopping service. To become a volunteer or to refer someone to the service contact the group.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,15