ce for people with a disability and their carers. Products and  services - A range of products and services tailor-made for the over 50s. Starting Point - a telephone helpline offering information and support to people aged 50 and over and  Support at Home Services - offering practical and emotional support in order for older people to retain their independence and volunteering - volunteers undertake a wide range of activities in our offices and in the community.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,150,1,1,53.548295,-2.633729,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'age-uk-wigan'),(401,'Home Instead Senior Care Wigan','Phil Eckersley','Pemberton Business Centre','Richmond Hill',NULL,'Wigan','WN5 8AA','01942 215888','phil.eckersley@homeinstead.co.uk','http://www.homeinstead.co.uk/wigan','Specialising in non-medical care of older people in their own homes, Home Instead Senior Care assists people to remain at home where they\'re most happy and comfortable; giving their families the freedom to relax in the knowledge that their loved ones are in excellent hands. We provide companionship, home help and personal care services tailored to an individual’s needs and requirements – providing a person centred holistic care service. We regard it as a special privilege to look after people with love, care and compassion - and we take our responsibilities very seriously indeed.',NULL,'HISC_Wigan','https://www.facebook.com/hiscwigan',1,150,1,1,53.537295,-2.67935,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'home-instead-senior-care-wigan'),(402,'Contact the Elderly','Kathleen Sheridan',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Greater Manchester',NULL,'0800 716543 or ','info@contact-the-elderly.org.uk','http://www.contact-the-elderly.org.uk/','Contact the Elderly is the only national charity solely dedicated to tackling loneliness and social isolation among older people. We aim to do this by organising monthly Sunday afternoon tea parties for small groups of older people (aged 75+) who live