se several events and social gatherings, as well as arranging outings to different places of interest both on the Island and the Mainland. Every member receives a monthly newsletter detailing all the forthcoming activities and events. We are involved in the Wootton Village Christmas Nativity event and in July, their &ldquo;Party in the Park&rdquo; which is held on the local recreation ground.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We take part in the various County and National Federation Competitions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We welcome new members to our friendly and active Institute, and have great fun in all we do. If you are interested in joining please contact us or just come along to one of our meetings held between 7.15 - 9.30pm on the 2nd Wednesday of each month at the Methodist Church in Station Road. You will be most welcome.&quot;</p>\r\n','2nd Wed of the month. 7.15pm','','',1,150,0,1,50.7155661,-1.24394989999996,'eng','2014-08-10 23:17:38','2014-09-04 16:54:15',NULL,NULL,'creekside-wi'),(669,'Bembridge Cricket Club','Mr Marston, Chairman ','Bembridge Community Hall','','','Bembridge','PO35 5UL','01983 873510','','http://bembridgecricket.hitscricket.com/','','','','',1,150,1,1,50.6853235,-1.08579480000003,'eng','2014-08-10 23:22:51','2014-09-04 16:53:51',NULL,NULL,'bembridge-cricket-club'),(670,'East Cowes Christian Centre','','Bridge House','1 Ferry Road','','East Cowes','PO32 6QY','','','','<p>Fair Trade Coffee Mornings.</p>\r\n','Mon: 10-12noon. ','','',1,150,1,1,50.7581229,-1.28873160000001,'eng','2014-08-10 23:29:26','2014-09-04 16:53:29',NULL,NULL,'east-cowes-christian-centre'),(671,'East Cowes Ladies Group','Janet Griffin','Methodist School Rooms','Yarborough Road','','East Cowes','','01983  291774','','','<p>Speakers, quizzes, etc. New members welcome.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&pound;2.00 per meeting</p>\r\n','Meet on the 2nd and 4th Tuesday of every month.','','',1,150,0,1,NULL,NULL,'eng','2014-08-10 23:35:24','2014-09-04 16:52:10',NULL,NULL,'east-cowes-ladies-group'),(