mes: Monday to Friday - 9am to 1pm','','',1,150,1,1,50.7243677,-1.2311995,'eng','2014-08-11 16:01:15','2014-09-04 15:51:54',NULL,NULL,'wootton-bridge-community-centre'),(709,'Wootton Health Walk','Richard Dent Volunteer Coordinator IOW NHS Trust','Wootton community centre ','Brannon Way','Wooton Bridge','Ryde','PO33 4NW','822099 ext 6246','richard.dent@iow.nhs.uk','','<p>Meet at Wootton community centre (winter) or outside parish council offices, Brannon way, Wootton</p>\r\n','every Thursday of the month at 2.30pm ','','',1,150,1,1,50.7243677,-1.2311995,'eng','2014-08-11 16:21:43','2014-09-04 15:49:16',NULL,NULL,'wootton-health-walk'),(710,'Yoga','Lisa Mckenzie','St Mary\'s Primary School','Ampthill Road','','Ryde','PO33 1LJ','07903363522','','','<p>Yoga and Relaxation-Mixed/All Levels</p>\r\n','Mon: 19:00-20:30','','',1,150,1,1,50.7268726,-1.14779380000005,'eng','2014-08-11 16:55:14','2014-09-04 15:45:07',NULL,NULL,'yoga-17'),(711,'Yoga','Rachel Price','Ryde Children\'s Centre, By Ryde Co-op','George Street','','Ryde','PO33 2JF','07796457855','','','<p>Hatha Yoga-All Abilities</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call on 01983 402505&nbsp;or</p>\r\n','Tues: 19:00-20:15','','',1,150,1,1,50.729454,-1.16150489999995,'eng','2014-08-11 16:57:02','2014-09-04 15:39:30',NULL,NULL,'yoga-18'),(712,'Yoga','Tulsi Nickie Short','Church Close Community Centre','Church Close','Wooton Bridge','Ryde','PO33 4QH','07799032824','','','<p>Satyanda Yoga-General</p>\r\n','Thurs: 09:30','','',1,150,1,1,50.7256771,-1.2361366999999701,'eng','2014-08-11 17:08:00','2014-09-04 15:39:02',NULL,NULL,'yoga-19'),(713,'Yoga','Judith Didham ','British Red Cross Hall','York Avenue','','East Cowes','PO32 6RU','01983 294203 ','info@Judithdidham.co.uk','http://www.judithdidham.co.uk/','<p>Hatha Yoga-Mixed</p>\r\n','Tues: 09:30-11.00am','','',1,150,1,1,50.7576386,-1.28747720000001,'eng','2014-08-11 17:12:35','2014-09-04 15:38:37',NULL,NULL,'yoga-20'),(714,'Yoga ','Tulsi Nickie Short','Binstead Methodist Church','Chapel Road','','Binstead','PO33 3RT','07799032824','','http://www.yogaisleofwight.co.uk/','<p>Satyamvidya Yoga - Beginners</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Courses cost &pound;50 for 7 weeks&nbsp;<br />\r\n<em>A number of subsidised places are available in each class, please let me know if you need financial assistance as I do not like to exclude anyone on the grounds of financial hardship.</em></p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Satyananda yoga&nbsp;classes are accessible for everyone regardless of age, gender, physical ability or experience, they emphasise the spiritual and meditative side of yoga and classes include:<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAsanas&nbsp;(postures) &ndash; a technique that when practiced regularly re-tones and revitalizes all the systems of the body. Asanas can be adapted to allow each individual to progress at their own pace, enabling challenge whilst respecting the needs and limitations of each individual.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPranayama&nbsp;(controlled, rhythmical and regular breathing) &ndash; all of us have to breath. These practices teach correct breathing and conserve and distribute prana (life force or vital cosmic energy) throughout the whole being, enhancing the power of the breath to help us feel energized, to move the body more effectively, to reduce tension, to help us sleep and to increase the awareness of breath.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYoga Nidra&nbsp;(psychic sleep or deep relaxation) &ndash; this is a powerful technique that creates psychic and physiological rest and rejuvenation. Relaxation is the key to reaching our potential. By learning different relaxation techniques each individual can begin to take control of their own life, relaxing, restructuring and reforming the whole personality from within.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nMeditation&nbsp;&ndash; &lsquo;meditation is an exercise in the mental discipline of harnessing the energies of the mind by focusing on one object or thought, or the breath, leading to increased concentration, a sense of peace and the release of tension.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nChanting&nbsp;- Mantra is vibration, and the compressed energies of the body and the mind respond to these vibrations. With these mantras, positive and creative qualities and energies can be awakened and negative influences removed. The use of sound and learning how to make sound vibrations is both liberating and relaxing.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nClasses follow a theme throughout each block of 6 or 7 weeks and although the structure of the class is similar each week, the contents take you through a journey of progression and self-awareness.</p>\r\n','Thursday 5.45pm Beginners, Thursday 7.30pm Intermediate','','',1,150,1,1,50.7266542,-1.1877656000000298,'eng','2014-08-11 17:15:30','2014-09-04 15:34:44',NULL,NULL,'yoga-21'),(715,'Yoga for Health Club, East Cowes','Ms Trish Wendes','43 Ash Road','','','Newport','PO30 2AQ','07866 182 678','','','<p>Or call;&nbsp;01983 533404</p>\r\n','Various','','',1,150,1,1,50.699277,-1.28775270000006,'eng','2014-08-11 17:18:44','2014-09-04 15:34:13',NULL,NULL,'yoga-for-health-club-east-cowes'),(716,'Yoga with Emma','Emma Spencer-Goodier','Haylands Primary School','Bettesworth Rd','','Ryde','PO33 3HA','01983  612545','','http://www.yogawithemma.co.uk/','<p>Beginners, Improvers, Ashtanga, private tuition</p>\r\n\r\n<p>8 week course is &pound;60, for the over 60yrs it is &pound;40, for students it is &pound;30. Drop ins are &pound;10 a class.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Call 01983 612545&nbsp;or 07880558599</p>\r\n\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<table style=\"width:546px\">\r\n	<tbody>\r\n		<tr>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">\r\n			<p>Day</p>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">\r\n			<p>Class Time</p>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">\r\n			<p>Date</p>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">\r\n			<p>Style</p>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-align: baseline\">\r\n			<p>Level</p>\r\n			</th>\r\n			<th style=\"vertical-a