elaxation, holistic therapies, good food club, coffee mornings, tai chi, discussion group, Spanish and IT.',NULL,'penlinkhouse','https://www.facebook.com/leigh.pensionerslink',1,150,1,1,53.497205,-2.513966,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'pensioners-link',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(107,133,'Leigh and District Camera Club',NULL,'99-101 Railway Road','Leigh',NULL,'Wigan','WN7 4AD','01942 879518','leighcameraclub@virginmedia.com','http://www.leighanddistrictcameraclub.org/index.html','Mondays 7:45pm and Thursdays 7:30pm. Further the art of photography; demonstrations, lectures, competitions internal and external with other clubs. £26 per annum.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,150,1,1,53.49714,-2.522583,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'leigh-and-district-camera-club',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(108,134,'Leigh Library',NULL,'Turnpike Centre','Civic Square','Market Street','Leigh','WN7 1EB','01942 404404','Leigh.Library@wlct.org','http://www.wlct.org/library-services/library-locations/leigh-library.htm','Mondays - Writers Group (fortnightly) 5:30pm – 6:45pm. A friendly and supportive creative writing session. Everyone Welcome. Leigh Family History Society 1:30pm – 3:30pm (Local History Desk). Tuesdays - My Guide 10am – 12 noon (In The Library) Internet course for beginners. Get into Reading 11:30pm - 1pm (In The Library), enjoy stories and poems read aloud, Bookchat 7:15pm - 9pm, Adult reading group runs on the 1st Tuesday in the month. Wednesdays - Carpe Diem Sewing Group 10am – 12noon (In The Derby Room). Thursdays - \'Chatterbooks\' - 11am – 12 noon 1st Thursday of the month. (In The Library), Your Bard (Shakespeare Reading Group) 5:30pm – 7pm. 4th Thursday of the month. (In The Derby Room), Poetry Reading Group 7:15pm – 8:30pm 2nd Thursday in month. Fridays - My Guide 10am – 12 noon Internet course for beginners. (In The Library). Saturdays - The Open Book Club 11am - 12noon (monthly). Reading group for adults. Re