e you the help, support and most importantly the motivation you will need to continue until you reach it. Success is a journey not a destination – come with us and enjoy the ride. If you can’t get to a Service, join our Slimming World Online programme.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,150,1,1,NULL,NULL,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'slimming-world',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(227,253,'Weight Watchers',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'0845 3451500','uk.help@weightwatchers.co.uk','http://www.weightwatchers.co.uk/index.aspx','Your food, your life, your weight loss. Our aim hasn’t changed over the years - it is simply to help you lose weight and learn how to keep it off. Because we believe that food is for life, for enjoyment and for good health, we have developed the new ProPoints plan using advanced weight loss science to give you a real weight loss advantage. Weight Watchers Meetings: Learn how to lose weight and keep it off with Weight Watchers meetings. Find out how the new ProPoints plan fits your life and makes losing weight even easier. Weight Watchers Online: Follow the new ProPoints plan completely online and learn how to lose weight and keep it off from the comfort of your own home. Ask your GP about the Weight Watchers Referral Scheme.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,150,1,1,NULL,NULL,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'weight-watchers',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(228,254,'Bolton Yoga Centre',NULL,'2 St Edmund Street',NULL,NULL,'Bolton','BL1 2JR','01204 238833','info@boltonyoga.co.uk','http://www.boltonyoga.co.uk/','We offer yoga classes, meditation and Tai Chi, which is great for people with lower mobility, to keep active. We are situated conveniently near the bus station and are on the ground floor. We also offer lots of other group activities and workshops. We also have plenty of chairs and could arrange to offer a specific chair based class in yoga/relaxation/meditation etc. The centre also offers therapy and healing t