don provides excellent access and leisure opportunities for all members of the community. At Fit City Clarendon there are fantastic swimming facilities. These comprise of a 25 metre pool that is shallow at both ends and a separate teaching pool. There is a health and fitness suite, a four court multi-purpose sports hall, aerobics studio, squash court and outdoor synthetic pitch. This centre is an Inclusive Fitness Initiative (IFI) accredited centre. This means that special consideration is given to people with disabilities. There are specially designated car parking spaces, easy ground floor access, modified exercise machines and a fully inclusive exercise programme.',NULL,'Sport_SC','https://www.facebook.com/pages/Salford-Community-Leisure/394597987283835',1,150,1,1,53.482914,-2.286624,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'fit-city-clarendon',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(303,329,'Fit City Eccles',NULL,'Barton Lane','Eccles',NULL,'Salford','M30 0DD','0161 7877107','fitcityeccles@scll.co.uk','http://www.salfordcommunityleisure.co.uk/sport/locations/fit-city-eccles','Fit City Eccles is a modern facility offering a double storey 85-station gym equipped with the latest range of Pulse Fitness cardiovascular and resistance equipment. There is a comprehensive range of aerobic classes including, circuits, spinning, aerobics, boxercise, chair based exercise classes and tai-chi. There are also aqua-fit classes in the swimming pool. The 25m swimming pool provides a comprehensive programme of swimming activities from general public sessions to lane swimming, and competitive club. The large sports hall provides the opportunity to enjoy a range of traditional sporting activities and coaching classes.',NULL,'Sport_SC','https://www.facebook.com/pages/Salford-Community-Leisure/394597987283835',1,150,1,1,53.478871,-2.346207,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'fit-city-eccles',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(304,330,'Fit City Wors