 but a few.',NULL,'Sport_SC','https://www.facebook.com/pages/Salford-Community-Leisure/394597987283835',1,150,1,1,53.450242,-2.415671,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'irlam-and-cadishead-leisure-centre',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(306,332,'Fit City Pendlebury',NULL,'Cromwell Road','Pendlebury',NULL,'Salford','M27 9SZ','0161 7931750','fitcitypendlebury@scll.co.uk','http://www.salfordcommunityleisure.co.uk/sport/locations/fit-city-pendlebury','Close to the centre of Swinton, Fit City Pendlebury has a 25 metre swimming pool which offers a wide range of aquatic activities from public swimming to swimming lessons for all ages and abilities. For the competitive swimmer, Swinton Swimming Club is based at this centre.  The swimming pool is an ideal venue for people with disabilities. There is a regular weekly session for this group, and the pool includes a hoist. It is also served by purpose built changing, toilet and showering facilities, all with easy access. We have an extensive fitness class programme which is delivered in our large sports hall. Classes include circuits, Boxercise, Zumba, Aerobics and many more. Our Fitness Suite has recently undergone a full refurbishment, which included the installation of state of the art Pulse Resistance and Cardio Vascular (CV) equipment. All CV equipment has it\'s own integrated Freeview TV.',NULL,'Sport_SC','https://www.facebook.com/pages/Salford-Community-Leisure/394597987283835',1,150,1,1,53.516161,-2.343715,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'fit-city-pendlebury',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(307,333,'PARiS (Physical Activity Referral in Stockport)','Michelle Childs',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Stockport',NULL,'0161 4820900','gpreferral@lifeleisure.net','http://www.lifeleisure.net/enterprise/lifeleisurestockportgpreferral','Physical Activity Referral in Stockport (PARiS) is the GP Exercise Referral scheme in Stockport, designed to help patients with moderate medical conditions