dvice on how to access reputable Domiciliary Care Agencies to help with everyday needs such as shopping, cleaning, ironing and low level personal care. In addition, if any other needs are identified by the Liaison Officer these will be discussed with you, and with your permission, you will be signposted to the appropriate service. If necessary a home visit can be arranged from our Liaison Service to further discuss your needs in the comfort of your own home. We aim to ensure that your requests are responded to within ten working days and aim to provide services within 28 days. Starting Point can also put you in touch with a number of local reputable companies and people who offer services at a reasonable charge: cleaning services, shopping services, foot and nail care, handymen, lunch clubs, companies that provide or prepare meals, joiners, plumbers, electricians, plasterers, tilers, painters and decorators, gardeners, benefit information and advice, laundry services - washing and ironing, hairdressers, dog walking, befriending, personal care, home security, and many others… If you would prefer, someone from Starting Point can visit you at home to discuss your needs in more detail.',NULL,NULL,NULL,1,150,1,1,53.542466,-2.641195,'eng','2013-05-20 12:00:00','2013-05-20 12:00:00',NULL,NULL,'starting-point-telephone-helpline-–-age-uk-wigan',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:01'),(391,417,'Groundwork Lancashire West and Wigan - Garden Squad Service','Kerry O\'Neil','74-80 Hallgate',NULL,NULL,'Wigan','WN1 1HP','01942 821444','kerry.oneil@groundwork.org.uk','http://www.groundwork.org.uk','The Garden Squad is a team of 5 operatives and a supervisor who provide a one off gardening service for people over 50 or who are registered disabled and unable to do the work themselves. They can provide a service in strimming, hedge trimming, weeding, mowing, fencing, basic flagging (of small areas) and other general landscaping tasks. The charges are £72 per day or £12 per hour. The customer 