4:53',NULL,NULL,'creative-writing-group',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:02'),(642,668,'Creekside WI','Lyn Forster ','Methodist Church','Station Road','','Wootton','PO33 4RR','01983 884128','info@creeksidewi.org.uk','http://creeksidewi.org.uk/','<p>&quot;Creekside today is a thriving Institute with 72 members. We meet at the Methodist Church in Station Road, Wootton at 7.15 pm on the second Wednesday of the month. We have an enthusiastic President and Committee who are dedicated to making everyone welcome at all the meetings, activities and events. In the church each month, we hold a business meeting followed by tea/coffee and home made biscuits, which gives us the opportunity to chat informally. There is normally a guest speaker and topics are varied and sometimes unusual.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>In between our monthly meetings we have a range of 11 different activities and members are welcome to attend as many or as few as they wish. Also during the year we organise several events and social gatherings, as well as arranging outings to different places of interest both on the Island and the Mainland. Every member receives a monthly newsletter detailing all the forthcoming activities and events. We are involved in the Wootton Village Christmas Nativity event and in July, their &ldquo;Party in the Park&rdquo; which is held on the local recreation ground.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We take part in the various County and National Federation Competitions.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>We welcome new members to our friendly and active Institute, and have great fun in all we do. If you are interested in joining please contact us or just come along to one of our meetings held between 7.15 - 9.30pm on the 2nd Wednesday of each month at the Methodist Church in Station Road. You will be most welcome.&quot;</p>\r\n','2nd Wed of the month. 7.15pm','','',1,150,0,1,50.7155661,-1.24394989999996,'eng','2014-08-10 23:17:38','2014-09-04 16:54:15',NULL,NULL,'creekside-wi',NULL,NULL,'2015-03-05 16:03:02'),(643,669,'Bembridge Cr